header.note: The source node in most cases contains the sample message as written by the developer. If it looks like a dot-delimitted string such as "form.label.firstname", then the developer has not provided a default message.

trans-unit.source: Are you sure you want to continue and overwrite the published version?
trans-unit.target: Êtes-vous absolument sûr(e) de vouloir continuer, et ainsi effacer la version publiée ?

trans-unit.source: To resolve the conflict, click Cancel and delete the draft. Then edit the published version.
trans-unit.target: Pour résoudre le conflit, cliquez sur Annuler et effacez le brouillon. Puis éditez la version publiée.

trans-unit.source: If you continue, the published version will be overwritten.
trans-unit.target: Si vous continuez la version publiée sera écrasée.
